Bollywood dialogues quiz is an interesting quiz game. If you are one of the Bollywood lovers you will the skill.

If you like the skill please leave a review and try once you'll love it. I'll try to give a weekly update and try to cover all the interesting Bollywood dialogues. This skill consists of top-rated Bollywood dialogues like "kitne aadmi the", "jo dar gya smjo mr gya", "Puspa, I hate tears" and so on.
